Expected 10th March

A DVD of the late great Lou Reed's 1983 solo performance in New York

“A Night With Lou Reed” was filmed in the intimate surroundings of the Bottom Line in New York City in 1983. The setlist features classic tracks from the Velvet Underground albums, through his classic “Transformer” and up to his then latest release “Legendary Hearts”. For Reed, born in Brooklyn and whose career began in Greenwich Village, this was a homecoming concert played before a packed audience and he delivered an outstanding performance.
